name: Blitzr
description: Blitzr provide methods to call API Blitzr

name: constructor
description: Create instance

params.name: keyAPI
params.description: An API Key is required to use all methods

name: search
description: Provide search methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.search.artist({ query: 'myQuery' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: radio
description: Provide radio methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const playlist = []
blitzr.radio.artist({ uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { playlist = res })

name: track
description: Provides track methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const track = {}
blitzr.track.get({ uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { track = res })

name: artist
description: Provide artist methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.artist.get({ uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: harmonia
description: Provide harmonia methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.harmonia.artist({ service_name: 'spotify', service_id: 'spotify_id' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: label
description: Provide label methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.label.get({ uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: release
description: Provide releases methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.releases.get({ uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: shop
description: Provide shop methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const result = []
blitzr.shop.artist('mp3', { uuid: 'uuid' }).then(res => { result = res })

name: tag
description: Provide tag methods - All methods return a promise
examples:
const tag = ''
blitzr.tag.get({ slug: 'slug' }).then(res => { tag = res })

name: event
description: Provide event method - return a promise
examples:
const event = {}
blitzr.event.get({ slug: 'slug' }).then(res => { event = res })

name: player
description: Create an instance of Player

name: key
description: Set a new API Key

name: key

name: play
